    "## 3. Format with chat template\n",
    "\n",
    "DPO Trainer expects `prompt / chosen / rejected` columns. Each must already\n",
    "include the chat template tokens — Trainer doesn't apply template internally."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 30,
   "id": "6b8fbd16",
   "metadata": {
    "colab": {
     "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
     "height": 66,
     "referenced_widgets": [
      "709f908d1c5e4f45a4f0a0608aa95b01",
      "5fab4ca59ba146f99c9eaf33dd64dee0",
      "f924d98898c747ee95f6729ce5abd8ed",
      "3de2ce9632254b8eb04ddbab5e4bcfba",
      "870e0523dc004a6294ba21ebf8644ddf",
      "56d838417dff45fa8ab2a242a54012ff",
      "ccc99931aff74c048ff32d5e7fef938c",
      "8c51ca7630d64869833d0fc4a72211a5",
      "abadf23bcca6491f90bb1c8aa7a493db",
      "7bccc5442bd34614986f1417ec889145",
      "d21c7295524847ce8c2e2a0445e7928a"
     ]
    },
    "id": "6b8fbd16",
    "outputId": "3e2b6852-497e-423c-cb31-f2517612f9c5"
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "output_type": "display_data",
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "Map:   0%|          | 0/2000 [00:00<?, ? examples/s]"
