        "id": "92df64cf"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 1. Load base model with Unsloth\n",
        "\n",
        "Unsloth bundles patched 4-bit kernels — that's how Qwen2.5-3B (or 7B) stays\n",
        "in T4 / A100 budget. The `FastLanguageModel.from_pretrained` call returns a\n",
        "4-bit quantized base; `get_peft_model` attaches the LoRA adapter on top."
      ]
    },
